{"tid":2398323,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國民眾不願接種國產疫苗 彭博：經濟前景面臨挑戰","createTime":"2021-02-07T07:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T09:06:59.000Z","uid":32511,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2f20538e3a385cac9c9ee909050a5c13de20e67c","tid":2398323,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T07:55:53.000Z","msg":"彭博新聞報導，中國推廣疫苗接種7周以來，實際接種的程度卻意外不如預期，遠不如美國、歐洲國家施打疫苗的進度：中國每100人接種僅2劑多一點，歐盟為3劑，美國為10劑，以色列接近60劑；此一結果將對中國經濟前景構成重大挑戰。<br />\n <br />\n彭博疫苗追蹤統計顯示，中國去年12月15日正式開始接種疫苗以來，迄今施打逾3120萬劑疫苗，對有14億人口的中國相當於每百人僅施打2劑，不如歐洲每百人約施打3劑、美國每百人施打10劑，更遠不及以色列每百人施打近60劑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3434767\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3434767&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOVYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=c7e195a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3434767&h=961ee93f\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3434767</a>"},{"pid":"8c7a7d724f8c187a9e7e4e39f7557695e4bbb576","tid":2398323,"uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T07:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xaKGRyA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxaKGRyA.jpg&h=2a00bf3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/euuYwXu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeuuYwXu.jpg&h=b3173665&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2587d83ba89081262287dfef7c2f2fc630a26866","tid":2398323,"uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T07:57:34.000Z","msg":"支那人都唔上當<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919125ec741d5f034071198b5325546c3b03d46b","tid":2398323,"uid":91397,"like":0,